      <title>澳大利亚Star Entertainment上半年利润下降43%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/australias-star-entertainment-logs-43-fall-first-half-profit-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚明星娱乐集团周四公布上半年利润下降，原因是这家现金短缺的赌场运营商受到消费者可自由支配支出疲软和竞争加剧的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/australias-star-entertainment-logs-43-fall-first-half-profit-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 22:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
