    <item>
      <title>两名巴基斯坦人因呼吁杀害荷兰极右翼领导人而受到指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/two-pakistanis-charged-over-calls-dutch-far-right-leaders-killing-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰一家法院表示，周三已对两名巴基斯坦国民提出指控，罪名是公开呼吁谋杀极右翼反穆斯林领导人基尔特·维尔德斯(Geert Wilders)，维尔德斯的政党在11月赢得选举后打算领导新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/two-pakistanis-charged-over-calls-dutch-far-right-leaders-killing-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 18:23:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>活动人士在阿联酋世贸组织会议上批评民间社会的“限制”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/activists-criticise-civil-society-restrictions-wto-meeting-uae-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周在阿拉伯联合酋长国举行的世界贸易组织（WTO）会议上，民间社会组织批评了对其参与的限制，包括声称其一些成员在会谈中被短暂拘留。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/activists-criticise-civil-society-restrictions-wto-meeting-uae-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 16:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>王储称挪威国王哈拉尔在医院感觉好些</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norways-king-harald-feeling-better-hospital-crown-prince-says-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威王储表示，挪威国王哈拉尔本周早些时候因感染在马来西亚住院后，周三似乎感觉好多了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norways-king-harald-feeling-better-hospital-crown-prince-says-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:27:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊姆兰的政党敦促国际货币基金组织确保在进行更多救助谈判之前完成巴基斯坦选举审计</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-party-urges-imf-consider-pakistans-instability-talks-sources-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦被监禁的前总理伊姆兰·汗所在的政党周三要求国际货币基金组织确保在与伊斯兰堡进行更多救助谈判之前对有争议的 2 月 8 日选举进行审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-party-urges-imf-consider-pakistans-instability-talks-sources-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿布扎比主权基金今年将投资太空技术和人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/abu-dhabi-sovereign-fund-invest-space-tech-ai-this-year-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比穆巴达拉投资公司董事总经理周三表示，今年将向人工智能和太空技术投入大量资金，并承诺该主权财富基金将在美国进行更多投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/abu-dhabi-sovereign-fund-invest-space-tech-ai-this-year-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚法院恢复对前总理穆希丁滥用职权的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-court-reinstates-abuse-power-charges-against-ex-pm-muhyiddin-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国家通讯社马新社报道，马来西亚上诉法院周三恢复了对反对党领袖和前总理穆希丁·亚辛滥用权力的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-court-reinstates-abuse-power-charges-against-ex-pm-muhyiddin-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登严厉打击美国数据流向中国和俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的政府周三公布了一项行政命令，禁止向中国传输基因组数据，出于国家安全考虑，寻求保护美国个人数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:02:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在医生抗议下将派遣军医前往医院</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-send-military-doctors-hospitals-amid-doctors-protest-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总理韩德洙周三表示，在实习医生大规模罢工后，韩国将在未来几天内派遣军队和社区医生前往医院，作为支持医疗保健系统的紧急措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-send-military-doctors-hospitals-amid-doctors-protest-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:24:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
